{"tid":1067770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"烏大龜一到店，","createTime":"2019-03-18T18:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T07:32:17.000Z","uid":208722,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0d5e9a7a75fdb306b867f42231b6532e0e072911","tid":1067770,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T18:06:53.000Z","msg":"以下開放接龍、討論甚至自行創作都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1a5441f36b6fe156b44a1b3ae131f115f0ea79","tid":1067770,"uid":236414,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T18:08:16.000Z","msg":"有的叫道，「烏大龜，你怎麼又回來學術台了！」<br />\n<br />\n他不回答，對櫃裡說，「溫兩碗酒，要一本教科書。」便排出九文大錢。<br />\n<br />\n他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又被膠登巴打趕出來了！」<br />\n<br />\n烏大龜睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你被眾巴打恥笑，吊著打。」<br />\n<br />\n烏大龜便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「退出不能算趕&hellip;&hellip;退出！&hellip;&hellip;IQ135的ENTJ，還會被趕麼？」<br />\n<br />\n接連便是難懂的話，什麼「Entering university is MK behavior」，什麼「中化考得好都是狗公」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"4e95f7e1661c884cf51d62a88160ae010a0652b3","tid":1067770,"uid":44073,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T18:35:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6734217b04f49d54814aa439d0356a351322c024","tid":1067770,"uid":44073,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T18:40:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e9163b6eebe884c8b8d39b2a468b2747ca85b29","tid":1067770,"uid":175598,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T18:50:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"111cea12ca5694f053d82c9b0f9001593a227855","tid":1067770,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T18:51:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c90a09818b3b3abf3a593600cedf422270700372","tid":1067770,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T19:39:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0cc3e2d8f4f7f74f21359406f7bc64cf4d455e60","tid":1067770,"uid":44073,"like":2,"dislike